{
  "1": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I, Isaiah son of Amoz, received from Yahweh this message about the city of Babylon:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "2": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Lift up a flag on the bare top of a hill,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "to signal that an army should come to attack Babylon.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Shout to them and wave your hand to signal to them\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "that they should march through the city gates into the palaces of the proud rulers of Babylon!\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "3": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Yahweh says, \"I have commanded those who are set apart to do this work for meâ€”\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I have summoned the warriors whom I have chosen to punish the people of Babylon because I am very angry with them,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and those soldiers will be very proud when they do that.\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "4": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Listen to the noise on the mountains,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "which is the noise of a huge army marching!\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "It is the noise made by people of many people groups shouting.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Yahweh, commander of the angel armies, has summoned this army to gather together.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "5": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "They come from countries that are far away,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "from the most remote places on the earth.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "They are like weapons that Yahweh will use to punish the people with whom he is very angry,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and to destroy the entire country of Babylonia.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "6": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "You people of Babylon will scream because you will be terrified,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "because it will be the time that Yahweh has determined,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "the time for the all-powerful God to destroy your city.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "7": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Because that will happen, all of your people will be very afraid,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "with the result that they will be unable even to lift their arms.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "8": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "All of you will be terrified.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "You will have severe pains\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "like a woman has when she is giving birth to a baby.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "You will look at each other helplessly,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and it will show on your faces that you feel horror.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "9": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Listen to this, you people of Babylon: The day that Yahweh has chosen to act in is near,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "the day on which he will furiously and fiercely punish you because he is very angry with you.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "He will cause your land of Babylonia to be desolate,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and he will destroy all the sinners in it.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "10": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "When that happens, none of the stars will shine.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "When the sun rises, it will be dark,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and there will be no light from the moon at night.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " \n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "11": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Yahweh says, \"I will punish everyone in the world for the evil things that they do;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I will punish the wicked people for the sins that they have committed.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I will stop arrogant people from being proud,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and I will stop cruel people from being so arrogant.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "12": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "And because I will cause most people to die,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "people will be harder to find than gold,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "harder to find than fine gold from Ophir in Arabia.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "13": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I will shake the sky,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and the earth will also move out of its place.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "That will happen when I, Yahweh, commander of the angel armies, punish wicked people,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "when I show them that I am extremely angry with them.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "14": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "All the foreigners in Babylon will run around like deer that are being hunted,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "like sheep that do not have a shepherd.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "They will try to find other people from their countries,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and then they will escape from Babylon and return to their own countries.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "15": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Anyone who is captured in Babylon\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "will be killed by their enemies' swords.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "16": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Their little children will be dashed to pieces on the rocks while their parents watch;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "their enemies will steal everything valuable from their houses and will force their wives to sleep with them.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "17": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Look! I am going to incite the people of Media to attack Babylon.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "The army of Media will attack Babylon, even if they are offered silver or gold if they promise to not attack it.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "18": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "With their arrows, the soldiers of Media will shoot the young men of Babylon;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "they will not even act mercifully toward infants or children!\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "19": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Babylon has been a very beautiful city;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "all the people of Babylonia have been very proud of Babylon, their capital city;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "but God will destroy Babylon,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "like he destroyed Sodom and Gomorrah.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "20": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "No one will ever live in Babylon again.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "It will be deserted forever.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Nomads will refuse to set up their tents there;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "shepherds will not bring their flocks of sheep to rest there.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "21": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Animals that live in the desert will be there;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "jackals will live in the ruins of the houses.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Owls will live in the ruins,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and ostriches and wild goats will romp around there.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "22": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Hyenas will howl in the ruined towers,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and jackals will make their dens in the ruins of the palaces that were previously very beautiful.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "The time when Babylon will be destroyed is very near;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Babylon will not exist much longer.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      }
    ]
  },
  "front": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "tag": "p",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "paragraph"
      }
    ]
  }
}